summary: a cheatbook simple book whit skyrim console commands buyable from court wizards
descriptionHtml:
A very useful mod wich adds a book whit skyrim console commands, so you don\'t have to exit the game to go and look up codes. Just open your inventory and find the cheat you need !! there a a lot of console commands so you will defently find the one you need . 

The Cheatbooks are buyable from court wizards in Markarth, Solitude, Whiterun and Riften i tested the mod and it works fine for me so you shouldn\'t have any problems.

The cheats in the book are from a web page http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/11/16/skyrim-console-commands-let-you-cheat-and-do-other-stuff/

hope you enjoy the FUN of cheats !!!!! :D
author: Alduin1998
